        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "To participate in lighting and shading, a geometry must include surface normal vectors in its vertex data. Some scene files may not contain such data. If you set this optionâ€™s value to "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/objectivec/yes"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": ", SceneKit applies heuristics to generate surface normal data for each geometry it loads from the scene source if such data is absent."
            }
          ]
        }
